[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_0",
    "text": "湖北省 鄂 武汉 青海省 青 西宁 宁夏回族自治区 宁 银川 新疆维吾尔自治区 新 写鲁木齐 香港特别行政区 港 香港 澳门特别行政区 澳 澳门 台湾省 台 台湾",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1292422129242213,
      0.13886146758802237,
      0.7364016736401674,
      0.35406383678841724
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_1",
    "text": "①跨纬度最广的是海南省。跨经度最广的是内蒙古自治区.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12645281264528127,
      0.3659098387627509,
      0.7140864714086471,
      0.38960184271141823
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_2",
    "text": "②地处纬度最高的是黑龙江省。纬度最低的是海南省.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12738261273826126,
      0.397499177360974,
      0.6601580660158066,
      0.4198749588680487
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_3",
    "text": "③少数民族数目最多的是云南省",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12366341236634124,
      0.4290885159591971,
      0.4509530450953045,
      0.4514642974662718
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_4",
    "text": "④大陆海岸线最长的是广东省。沿海岛屿最多的是江省.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12831241283124128,
      0.4593616321158276,
      0.7131566713156672,
      0.4823955248436986
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_5",
    "text": "⑤全部处于热带的是海南省",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1292422129242213,
      0.4922671931556433,
      0.4119014411901441,
      0.5139848634419217
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_6",
    "text": "⑥邻国最多的是新疆维吾尔自治区。邻省最多的是内蒙古自治区，陕西省. ②面积最大的是新疆维吾尔自治区、面积最小的是澳门特别行政区 ⑧人口最多的是河南省，人口最少的是澳门特别行政区。 ⑨同时涉临黄、渤海的是辽宁省、山东省. 北回归线自西向东穿过的省是云南省.广西壮族自治区、广东省.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11808461180846118,
      0.5185916419874959,
      0.8823802882380288,
      0.6686410003290556
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_7",
    "text": "众多的人口",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.1097164109716411,
      0.7101020072392235,
      0.21478382147838215,
      0.7298453438631128
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_8",
    "text": "1.世界上人口最多的国家",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11622501162250116,
      0.7416913458374466,
      0.3403068340306834,
      0.7640671273445212
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_9",
    "text": "(1)据2000年第五次人口普查，我国总人口为12.95亿，占世界人口总数的115以上。2005年1月6 日.为中国的3亿人口日.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11157601115760112,
      0.771964461994077,
      0.9409576940957695,
      0.8265876933201711
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_10",
    "text": "(2)人口的突出特点：人口基数大，人口增长快.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14690841469084148,
      0.8344850279697269,
      0.5532310553231056,
      0.8562026982560053
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58_11",
    "text": "(3)人口政第：实行计划生育是我国的一项基本国策。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14690841469084148,
      0.8654162553471537,
      0.6183170618317062,
      0.8871339256334321
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_58",
    "order": 12
  }
]